## Alt Table 3: Data Moments

In particular, this section focuses on the method used to complete Table
3 (data). We chose to use US data. In this version, I used the working
age population as my population variable. I was also advised to alter
the quarter period from 1982-04-01 - 2025-12-31 to 1982-01-01 -
2025-07-01. I get extremely similar results. I presume this is due to
the logging and HP filter.

I will note the differences in results through my commits in Git. These
results do not seem to deviate very much from my initial findings and
so, primary markdown. Final big change was the variables used to
generate the gross quarterly inflation. I am sure this will alter the
results in the direction I’d been hoping for.

